# Prebuilt native binaries — produced by `napi build` and assembled into
# per-platform npm packages by the release workflow; never committed.
*.node
node_modules/
# napi-rs generates these beside the native translation crate, but the public
# loader and declarations live in packages/bindings. Keep the generated shim
# out of the repository so it cannot become a second public surface.
index.js
index.d.ts
pnpm-lock.yaml
